        "Biometric authentication",
        "Encrypted storage",
        "Secure DID management",
        "Credential presentation via QR codes and deeplinks",
        "Proximity-based interactions",
        "Credential filtering and search",
        "Customizable activations and visual alerts",
        "Backup and recovery",
        "Document signing integrations",
        "Multi-language support",
        "Selective disclosure"
